Tenṭeq-d seg teɛrict.
Lmenṭaq ur nris, mxellel ur nebgis.
Taqemmuct tesseblaɛ, ṣṣuṛa tessexlaɛ.
Rebbaɣ fell-as tasa.
Ečč lḥeqq-ik, sider i tiṭ-ik.
Anda akken ḍemɛeɣ tixsi, i nsiɣ mebla imensi.
Ur yettnecṛaḥ ḥedd d uɣyul-is.
D ayen tensa tmes-nni;
Yenna wagu, yenna waḍu.
Rẓag am qlilu.
Ɣas berriket tzizwit, tament-is ẓidet.
Qeḍran ma yezwer s imi, tament ma teggra-d i wumi.
Iles aẓidan, iteṭṭeḍ tasedda.
Adfel deg udrar, ssemm-is deg uẓaɣar.
Ad ak-yefk Ṛebbi, tazmert n tzemmurt.
Ad ak-yesuffeɣ Ṛebbi ɣar lebɣi n wul-ik.
Fkiɣ-ak talaba n sser.
Ad am-yekkes Ṛebbi aɣilif akka iyi-t-tekkseḍ.
Anwa i d ameẓẓuɣ-ik ay aɣerbi.
Lebɣi yella, ifadden kkawen.
Yal wa akken yura deg twenza-s.
Win ur nesɛi tagmat meḥqur.
Atmaten d atmaten, aɛubbuḍ yebḍa-ten.
Am uzrem, ɣef uɛebbuḍ kan i ileḥḥu.
La d-tettecrurud am tsekkurt.
Irden izellafen, mmi d ssmid yufafen.
Mfezwan am yibawen ɣef lluḥ.
Ad as-rreɣ tablaḍt i wul.
Teqqur tasa-s!
Iṛuḥ wul ad d-yekkes lxiq, yufa-n leḥbab d imuḍan.
